      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride with plenty of life left? This car is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear from its time on the road, it remains a solid choice for anyone seeking a functional and spirited vehicle. With a bit of your personal touch, this car will continue to be a reliable companion for all your travels!",
