    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, functional condition and serves as a practical choice for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading in the clear coat on the roof, and a few small dings on the passenger side doors. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and the driver's seat shows significant bolster wear, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain operational. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it lacks the tightness of a newer model and may require some minor suspension work in the near future. It is a solid, honest car that is ready for daily use.",
      "price": 21000.0,
