    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true showroom-quality masterpiece, meticulously maintained and kept in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no chips, swirls, or imperfections, complemented by flawless alloy wheels. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple without a single crease, and all high-tech interfaces function with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete service history of preventative maintenance performed exclusively by certified specialists. Every seal, gasket, and component is in peak condition, ensuring a driving experience that is as tight and responsive as the day it was manufactured. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector to acquire a vehicle that has been treated with the highest level of care and respect.",
      "price": 48900.0,
